{"tid":1564091,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"尖咀良心邊爐推介-漁一海鮮火鍋料理","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T09:57:42.000Z","uid":87724,"like":67,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c2cdae885a6b467b62cf66c4ee653a57ef9295","tid":1564091,"uid":87724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"今日同朋友出尖沙咀食飯，喺巴打之前整嘅黃藍Google Map搵食，搵倒間良心邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我朋友一入鋪頭就好唔客氣咁問老細你哋係咪黃㗎？老細都好唔客氣咁話，係呀我哋係黃㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知道係同道中人，就即刻坐低。<br />\n<br />\n坐低無耐，老細就送咗碟椒鹽蝦腐比我哋，話係同道中人請我哋食嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C64N1BR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC64N1BR.jpg&h=3cbd5dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個蝦腐好好食，熱辣辣有鑊氣<br />\n<br />\n啲邊爐料都好新鮮好大份，同有驚喜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oW9qOht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoW9qOht.jpg&h=ed32df73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋叫咗個杏汁豬肺湯底，開頭以為會好似熱杏霜咁臭，但飲落無臭味仲好潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後埋單老細又好唔客氣咁話大家同道中人比我八折我哋，埋單每人二百零蚊咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後同老細傾開，原來佢哋諗住嚟緊會派飯劵比小朋友，等佢哋唔洗挨肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我見間鋪頭成晚得幾枱客，樓下間7仔仲多客過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為和理非嘅你，真係要大大力、好唔客氣咁用錢懲罰呀老細，唔係佢邊有錢派飯比小朋友呀？<br />\n<br />\n[url]漁一海鮮火鍋料理<br />\r\n網上訂座享6折優惠兼賺里數    <br />\r\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0QsO900~uwvbiAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0QsO900~uwvbiAw&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=80700d24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0QsO900~uwvbiAw</a><br />\r\n地址: 尖沙咀寶勒巷3-7A號萬事昌廣場2樓1號舖<br />\r\n電話: 63143288<br />\r\n=====================<br />\r\n憑恒生信用卡於喜來登酒店、萬麗海景酒店及康得思酒店可享低至5折！優惠附帶條款。借定唔借？還得到先好借！[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDzVq84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDzVq84.jpg&h=bc5f3a55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bf0637502fc86b23a9f051ab8205974ad521423","tid":1564091,"uid":71090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:42:52.000Z","msg":"望落唔錯 下次試下"},{"pid":"b815ded088ad8f60fa380074f20336816e602d32","tid":1564091,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"cf870a3215764d39b92df606f899ffc24cc90a0e","tid":1564091,"uid":217679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"Ok 同老婆會去幫襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7a6be0a05f1ca36195213601c25cdeacb59493","tid":1564091,"uid":1797,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打手樣出晒黎"},{"pid":"b4d3e63bc31130f8b0fb130fb765fba99bf0b0f3","tid":1564091,"uid":238973,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:43:21.000Z","ms